narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a lot of vocabulary and grammar. Also learned a lot about industries in South Africa and how to present numerical information on them in Zulu.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: As always, the instructor excels at not just making this course a course about a language. There's really no point in taking a language course when you don't even understand the underlying culture and history of the language. In Zulu, we are able to learn about South Africa and its rich history.
Great learning environment - very engaging class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If you want to fulfill the language requirement, this is literally your best choice.
